data.description: Welcome Home! This 3BR/2BA home with an amazing kitchen is just what you have been looking for! The 3 bedroom, 2 bath split level floor plan, open living concept home is located in the sought after Bayside community.  Entertaining will be breeze in the gorgeous custom kitchen with modern elements. The stainless steel hood, gas range and oven, gigantic, functional island, sleek drawer cabinets and large, gorgeous brushed satin pulls, glass wall, and quartz counters are a chef's dream! Durable popular luxury vinyl tile floors in almost every room. Walls, doors, and trim have been freshly painted a cool light gray. The living, kitchen, and dining areas all open to one another. Custom light fixtures, recessed cans, and vaulted ceilings give this home a rich feel. In the back of the home, you'll find the master suite with entry through French doors. The master bedroom is home to a walk-in closet and another set of glass French doors that open up to a patio where you can enjoy morning coffee in your privately fenced yard. The master bathroom has a tiled walk in shower and double sink vanity. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath are located on the front of the home- one bedroom with a bay window that gives a considerable amount of soft, natural light to the room. A 30-year dimensional shingle roof was put on in 2016. Bayside is a charming neighborhood with nicely manicured common areas and amenities that include a community pool and park. Silver Sands Premium Outlets, Grand Boulevard, restaurants, and Sacred Heart Hospital are a short drive. A quick walk two blocks north is where the neighborhood bayfront park and dock for fishing, boating and water-based activities are found. Less than a mile away is the sugar white sand of Miramar Beach.
